Abstract interface for external storage - to be implemented by various backends
and registered in :py:class:`QgsExternalStorageRegistry`.

.. versionadded:: 3.22
%End

%TypeHeaderCode
#include "qgsexternalstorage.h"
%End
  public:

    virtual ~QgsExternalStorage();

